https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Racketeer_Influenced_and_Corrupt_Organizations_Act

Some of the alleged conspirators caught-up in Jan6 could be prosecuted under RICO because they engaged in:

- obstruction (of Justice) by attempting to stop the Senate from doing its job

- fraud by claiming election stolen, raising funds on same then putatively to find fraud but instead directed to other purposes

- possibly bribes by promising to pay legal fees or coopting behavior through Presidential pardons

- (domestic) terrorism by attacking the Capitol

all of which are included in RICO. Plus Jan6 in aggregate were multi-state including known organizations like the Proud Boys.
